nodes.text: "The Triple Dark" (German title "Invasion der Piraten") is a comic strip written by Alec Worley, drawn by Bob Molesworth and edited by Gunther Nickel. The story was published in the 3rd issue of the German Star Wars Resistance Animation-Magazine, released on September 18, 2019.
The comic partially adapts the episode of the same name of the television series Star Wars Resistance.
